videos.headline: Brewer leaps over defense for TD
videos.description: Baylor's QB Charlie Brewer takes a risky leap over the wall of defenders to score a 1-yard touchdown, giving his team a greater lead over Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brewer leaps over defense for TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lovett finds a gap and takes it 28 yards
videos.description: John Lovett patiently waits for an opening, then he turns on the speed for a 28-yard rushing touchdown putting Baylor on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lovett finds a gap and takes it 28 yards) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
